  "3088180": {
    "name": "Waffle Cone Willie",
    "steam_appid": 3088180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/583ee9cc7b6fbb1795d159e8998fded5.poster.avif?t=1730508436\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/583ee9cc7b6fbb1795d159e8998fded5.webm?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/583ee9cc7b6fbb1795d159e8998fded5.mp4?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>欢迎来到甜水镇，这曾是一个理想的郊区社区，如今却笼罩在恐怖之中。《华夫甜筒威利》是一款第一人称生存恐怖游戏，玩家必须躲避一个被幽灵附身的杀人冰淇淋车，并揭开隐藏在阴影中的邪恶秘密。<br>在甜水镇，从一栋房子跑到另一栋房子，藏匿并潜行，揭开谜团，解决难题，在华夫甜筒威利的不断追捕中生存下来，直到你收集到所需的一切，最终面对威利并逃离这个噩梦。<br><br>曾经深受喜爱的冰淇淋车司机、被判有罪的杀人犯威利的幽灵，变成了一种意想不到的可怕形式。这个恶意的灵魂占据了一辆旧冰淇淋车，被称为华夫甜筒威利，在街道上游荡，散播恐惧和混乱。<br><br>在甜水镇探索的每个家庭的安全只是假象，因为你会发现镇上越来越多的超自然威胁和活动，需要谨慎行事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/cf2c0a13b4275d39393c657c2775bfef.poster.avif?t=1730508436\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/cf2c0a13b4275d39393c657c2775bfef.webm?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/cf2c0a13b4275d39393c657c2775bfef.mp4?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>生存与潜行：</strong><br>通过蹲伏和避免被杀人冰淇淋车发现来躲避追踪。倾听卡车令人毛骨悚然的叮当声，藏在房子或阴影中，避免被发现。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/9f04f7a45f983c999f3d70030050494e.poster.avif?t=1730508436\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/9f04f7a45f983c999f3d70030050494e.webm?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/9f04f7a45f983c999f3d70030050494e.mp4?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>探索与解谜：</strong><br>探索甜水镇内的各种房屋和地点，每个地方都充满了秘密和危险。解决环境谜题以解锁新区域，找到重要线索，并拼凑出华夫甜筒威利的谜团。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/0eafd4d6589c6638995e415061ac665d.poster.avif?t=1730508436\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/0eafd4d6589c6638995e415061ac665d.webm?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/0eafd4d6589c6638995e415061ac665d.mp4?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>动态AI：</strong><br>体验威利的自适应AI带来的寒冷挑战，AI会学习并应对你的战术，使你在小镇中导航时保持高紧张感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/956f233cb11aa9a6a144e0e236cd0589.poster.avif?t=1730508436\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/956f233cb11aa9a6a144e0e236cd0589.webm?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088180/extras/956f233cb11aa9a6a144e0e236cd0589.mp4?t=1730508436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>氛围元素：</strong><br>沉浸在紧张、诡异的氛围中，声音和视觉提示提升恐怖感。卡车的冰淇淋扭曲的叮当声营造氛围，随着它的接近变得更加危险，提示你需要躲藏或逃跑。<br><br>你准备好面对徘徊在甜水镇的恶意力量了吗？在《华夫甜筒威利》中，每一个决定都可能意味着生与死的区别。你会揭开真相并幸存下来，还是会成为华夫甜筒威利的又一个受害者？",
